room_title: Escape room "The Council" by Suite Escape in Amarillo
room_description: The tension between the Dwarves and Elves is reaching a tipping point, and war seems imminent. The humans have stepped in to take over the peace talks with a council of the great men and women in the Kingdom. What is causing this strife, and how will you keep the attacks from occurring? You have one hour left to escape the council suite to reach the Dwarf King and Elven Elders to prevent a senseless war.
